c: 11
v: 66
t: ‘Oh ban troh bala Saleh meupeuglah ‘Oh ban troh bala Kamoe bri keunan Meupeungkleh yohnyan Saleh meutuah Ngon ureueng mukmin nyang sajan gopnyan Bandum ureueng nyan Kamoe peuleupah Kamoe bri rahmat bandum ureueng nyan Azeub uroenyan Kamoe peusiblah Keubit Po gata kuat ngon teuga Maha Perkasa hana ban peugah